<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Aw Nang Bethlehem</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal lung bukimna, kipah ni.
 Tuhin I tung kit tau;
 Va chieh leu hing Bethlehem daikieng ah.
 Van mi zaila sakna.

[V2]
 Aw, nang Bethlehem, ka hun ngaina zen e!
 Na tang chunga Puipa Aksi vak chu;
 Kap in hun hawl pek ding ka hi,
 Ka Lal pienna lei mun siepen chu.

[V3]
 2. Ngailo a um dem zie mun chu,
 Ka Lal sieng A lawihna;
 Kaisar lallai nitum kawl eng nuoiah,
 Ka Lal naubang kap ie.

[V4]
 3. Vak en tiem u, Angeltehaw
 Na lawppau Lal Isu;
 A hung tungtai gimthei chate nawpna,
 Pakbang chawian hitiu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>4</hymn_number>
<author>Patea</author>
</song>